com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface SolverLpParams

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, com.misc.common.moplaf.job.RunParams, SolutionProviderParams, SolverParams
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SolverLp
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SolverLpImpl, SolverLpParamsImpl

    public interface SolverLpParams
extends SolverParams
    A representation of the model object 'Lp Params'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Solver Optimality Tolerance
    • Solver Linear Relaxation
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getSolverLpParams()
